                    [artistname] => Dave Angus
                    [artisttext] => David Angus is a con-temporary artist primarily working with photography and video, although his practice has developed incorporating performance and sculpture. His work deals primarily with light, space and time. Exploring spaces defined by light and examining how light is used to define a pictorial image, through this experimentation light becomes a theatrical intervention and servers as a device in the creation of his work.
