                    [bio2] => <strong>Ausbildung:</strong><br>- 2002-2005 HKB (Hochschule der Künste Bern), BA (Hons) Visual Arts <br>- 2010-2011 Residency at the Rijksakademie van beeldende kunsten, Amsterdam
                    [bio3] => <strong>Weitere Informationen:</strong><br><a href="http://www.ovra-archives.com/pitteloud_annaik">www.ovra-archives.com/pitteloud_annaik</a>
                )

