                                    [viddate] => 2007, Albert Triviño Massó
                                    [vidtext] => 1’09“, Loop<br> Printed images on 16mm, ed. 5<br> <br> Printed strips into 16 mm transparent film. The piece is based on the repetition of the sequence GREEN-RED-BLUE where each word is one frame: GREEN with red letters in blue background. RED with blue letters and green background and BLUE with green letters and red background. 3 Colours is an experiment about language.
